THE HARLEM RIVER NO. 1. THE MARGARET MONK. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. April 6, 1925. No. 290. Alexander & Ash, of New York City (Edward Ash, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. *120Richard F. Lenahan, of New York City, for claimant of -the Margaret Monk.

Before ROGERS, MANTON, and HAND, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree affirmed, on the opinion in the court below.
